      },
      "geo": {
        "@type": "GeoCoordinates",
        "latitude": 43.657538,
        "longitude": -79.400202
      }
    },
    "description": "The Yacht Rock Show Canada is an authentic tribute to the 70s and 80s Classic Smooth Rock Era that defined a generation.\n\n Experience an unforgettable musical voyage, dancing and listening to classic hits from artists including: Toto, Styx, The Doobie Brothers, Michael McDonald, Christopher Cross, Kenny Loggins, Steely Dan, Boz Scaggs, Player, Little River Band, Ambrosia.\n\nThe El Mocambo is a legendary live music and entertainment venue in Toronto, Canada, that has hosted countless world-famous artists since it opened in 1948, including The Rolling Stones, Elvis Costello, Blondie, The Ramones, and Stevie Ray Vaughan. The new El Mocambo features state-of-the-art sound and lighting, a recording studio, and multiple floors for events and performances, offering a modern, VIP live music experience while maintaining its historical significance.",
    "url": "https://buy.pressplaytickets.com/yrs-elmo/",
    "image": "https://s3.ca-central-1.amazonaws.com/c3api-penguin-prod-toronto-storagestack-oc9o88-uploads/t07vrfwJpDyv5dOTHQ4x6A",
    "organizer": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "",
      "email": null,
      "telephone": null
    },
    "isAccessibleForFree": false,
    "keywords": [
