    "description": "Check out our website for an overview deck to learn more about me, and both our organization and project.\n\nIn essence, TISAS 26 is a globally focused Street Art conference meets mural festival in one, with a speakers plus workshop series, live mural painting as a spectator sport, A film festival, family programming, music , and more. its big, to say the least! We're inviting over 100 of the world's best and brightest street artists to participate in painting, speaking and teaching, bringing new color city wide.",
